Geordie-Greep.-CREDIT_-Elena-Di-Vincenzo_Archivio-Elena-Di-Vincenzo_Mondadori-Portfolio-via-Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Geordie-Greep.-CREDIT_-Elena-Di-Vincenzo_Archivio-Elena-Di-Vincenzo_Mondadori-Portfolio-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Geordie-Greep.-CREDIT_-Elena-Di-Vincenzo_Archivio-Elena-Di-Vincenzo_Mondadori-Portfolio-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Geordie-Greep.-CREDIT_-Elena-Di-Vincenzo_Archivio-Elena-Di-Vincenzo_Mondadori-Portfolio-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Geordie-Greep.-CREDIT_-Elena-Di-Vincenzo_Archivio-Elena-Di-Vincenzo_Mondadori-Portfolio-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Geordie-Greep.-CREDIT_-Elena-Di-Vincenzo_Archivio-Elena-Di-Vincenzo_Mondadori-Portfolio-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Geordie-Greep.-CREDIT_-Elena-Di-Vincenzo_Archivio-Elena-Di-Vincenzo_Mondadori-Portfolio-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/geordie-greep">Geordie Greep</a>邀请了肖恩·斯蒂芬斯（Sean Stephens），他在舞台上与他一起表演的病毒曲目“我是矩形”背后的歌手。查看下面的录像。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/geordie-greep-new-sound-album-review-black-midi-3799535">Geordie Greep  - “新声音”评论：令人眼花and乱的音乐性淹没了很多想法</a></strong></li></ul><p>史蒂芬斯（Stephens）在2023年首次欣赏这首歌，<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CurV21OvhJk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">他在世界各地徒步旅行，以促进</a>lipsy，在标志性的旅游目的地为Tiktok和Instagram发行。</p><p>尽管受到许多在线的许多人的嘲笑，但它在前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-midi">黑人Midi</a>主持人中找到了一个粉丝，他以前<a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@nts_radio/video/7428231408092515617" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在NTS广播电台的一次采访中</a>讨论了他对“随机”曲目的钦佩。从那时起，他甚至<a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@greepgreepgreep/video/7430228335881407776" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在表演时就加入了即兴演奏</a>。</p><p>在星期五（1月24日），格里普（Greep）对病毒的兴趣更进一步，在纳什维尔（Nashville）的演出中欢迎史蒂芬斯（Stephens）在舞台上。</p><p>音乐会表演的剪辑史蒂芬斯（Stephens）在Greep和他的乐队开始演奏“矩形”时走过人群。然后，他在舞台上爬上麦克风，然后唱着标志性的开场直线：“<em>我是矩形/我在骨头上感觉到它/我是矩形/我没有洞</em>。”</p><p>在下面查看。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DFQpFPfvVBb/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.65